# PulsarFab License

This repository contains both firmware/software and hardware design files, each under different licenses appropriate to their domain.

## Firmware and Software

All firmware and software code (including but not limited to files in the `firmware/` directory) is licensed under the **Apache License 2.0**.

See [firmware/LICENSE](firmware/LICENSE) for the full license text.

## Hardware Designs

All hardware design files, including:
- 3D models (CAD files, STL, STEP, etc.)
- PCB designs (schematics, layouts, Gerber files)
- Mechanical drawings
- Assembly instructions

are licensed under the **CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S v2)** with the following additional restriction:

**Non-Commercial Use Only.** You may not use, distribute, or modify the hardware designs for commercial purposes without prior written permission from the copyright holder. Commercial use includes manufacturing for sale, offering as a commercial product or service, or incorporating into commercial products.

The full CERN-OHL-S v2 license text is available at: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.txt

---

## Quick Summary

### Firmware (Apache 2.0)
- Commercial use allowed
- Modification allowed
- Distribution allowed
- Patent use allowed
- Must include copyright notice
- Must include license text
- Must state changes made

### Hardware (CERN-OHL-S v2 + Non-Commercial)
- Non-commercial use only
- Modification allowed (must share alike)
- Distribution allowed (non-commercial, must share alike)
- Must include copyright notice
- Must include license text
- Must document modifications
- Must distribute under same terms

